title: W.D. Stevens - A Midwinter's Nightmare (album released 16/7/2013
description:
A Midwinter's Nightmare by W.D. Stevens
(dedicated to Roma Slee)

Returning to the old days of classic rock and the British invasion in a modern setting with his debut album - W.D. Stevens!

1. Still Not Over You
2. Not Good Enough For You 
3. Breaking Free
4. Losing My Faith
5. Distance
6. Helpless to You
7. The Legacy (with Roma Slee)
8. Simplicity
9. Reflections
10. Jealousy

11. Jealousy [Live] (performed by "The Vibe")
12. Breaking Free [Live] (performed by "The Vibe")
